{"tid":1234423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢次真係贏得漂亮， 我哋要贏民心呀！","createTime":"2019-06-17T02:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T05:36:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d52cb2cda69098b276481f67177f095d3fc2ff","tid":1234423,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"呢次真係贏得漂亮， 我哋要贏民心呀！<br />\n<br />\n見到有啲人自己慢慢由夏愨道行去番去添美道方向，<br />\n<br />\n希望唔會影響啲中立或者未知咩事嘅人， 要慢慢拉埋佢哋嚟我哋呢邊，<br />\n起碼唔會大力反對我哋先。<br />\n<br />\n又見到啲人自己清潔馬路。<br />\n<br />\n呢次真係贏得漂亮。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次再嚟一定得到更多人支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家加油。"},{"pid":"c5c9129cfd119febfb4b72b0c7a1112ba172cb7a","tid":1234423,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"e95ad3f85603c78a0caf5dc86b00d8f819ef3ed5","tid":1234423,"uid":88587,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:12:42.000Z","msg":"贏你老母咩"},{"pid":"e43665f9269e5413014b13acc3f457e7b68cca8c","tid":1234423,"uid":18283,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:12:43.000Z","msg":"贏你老母臭閪 完全封鎖"},{"pid":"016f3763a411fda50fcdd87496fe2985dc3dace5","tid":1234423,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:13:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">未贏</span></span>"},{"pid":"cbc60625818dfeb610c2d1eb0c2c1b36a849794b","tid":1234423,"uid":28068,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"樓主on9已confirm..."},{"pid":"bfcab263ad37220ebb759f3f514b9f242b316a16","tid":1234423,"uid":13754,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:13:29.000Z","msg":"英超踢38場先有冠軍，而我哋只係踢咗幾場互有得失嘅波，未去到4月都未知冠軍花落誰家<br />\n<br />\n如果而家只係因為有失波，有黃牌就覺得失敗<br />\n<br />\n咁你同考第二都會喊嘅林鄭有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家放棄行動一兩次就會有成果嘅期望，預備自己去打持久戰<br />\n<br />\n1. 鍛鍊身體，令自己更強壯，保護自己，保護我哋嘅兄弟姊妹<br />\n2. 學定急救，噚日遊行嘅急救人手真係好唔夠<br />\n3. 去睇敵人對付我哋嘅方法，我哋一齊去諗策略<br />\n<br />\n我哋只要堅持，我哋只會離成功愈嚟愈近，離失敗愈嚟愈遠，唔好忘記曼德拉坐咗咁耐監，佢冇放棄<br />\n<br />\n佢喺監獄日日健身做掌上壓，就係為咗迎接勝利嘅一日"},{"pid":"7469ae37a7b48914021b13916c8e8c28964e3de5","tid":1234423,"uid":174530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:13:51.000Z","msg":"5:0！"},{"pid":"875d0e2847e71c487288b329a8bc6ec4c4c3c7f2","tid":1234423,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e43665f9269e5413014b13acc3f457e7b68cca8c","tid":1234423,"uid":18283,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:12:43.000Z","msg":"贏你老母臭閪 完全封鎖"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:14:09.000Z","msg":"真係child登<br />\n<br />\n有無分析過當年佔中失敗原因？"},{"pid":"11081b7b47dac17709b8144ef61850fcec9fb3b2","tid":1234423,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:14:26.000Z","msg":"失敗主義不是無為的理由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234103</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n希望經過今次大家學識抱打不平，友善照舊，有錯就要講！<br />\n<br />\n分化輿論要由我地親手阻止<br />\n<br />\n戰場唔止熱門仲有係最新"},{"pid":"c156e1c0504986d78426e0bcacd859b93269d67d","tid":1234423,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:14:29.000Z","msg":"打少陣飛機, 依家除左多左封道歉新聞稿, 乜柒都冇, 贏左乜撚請問"},{"pid":"4ff8c74d5e945edc76b5e46b80e3238fb0c2c17a","tid":1234423,"uid":156771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:14:31.000Z","msg":"曲到圓"},{"pid":"04b32cac8d1938c3879474c9f3539a1d46c524bd","tid":1234423,"uid":4875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:14:36.000Z","msg":"唔撚好用贏字！<br />\n<br />\n班飯民又唔識要求林鄭正面回應<br />\n連登就個個一味話影響民心，唔識推翻個波比林鄭"},{"pid":"ccc9450e09ddd68c4eebf8b1e393db64a742fbc0","tid":1234423,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T02:14:36.000Z","msg":"贏你老母<br />\n收嗲啦<br />\n係輸緊啊！<br />\n乜都冇爭取到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" cl